data.description: $15,000 total Price Improvement! Traditional 2 story home with 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a partial basement. Living room, formal dining room, and family room have beautiful hardwood floors, just take a peak under! Spacious kitchen featuring tile backsplash, lots of cabinetry, plenty of countertop space and custom built-in pantry. 2nd-floor primary bedroom with a large walk-in closet and a private bath. 3 more generously sized bedrooms on the upper level with two featuring walk-in closets. Basement is complete and currently used as a bedroom but has a finished area for an additional rec room or living room. Fenced-in backyard with a large shed . Only a short drive from Armstrong Park with a pond, walking trails, athletic fields, tennis courts, and Castaway Bay aquatic center. Conveniently close to restaurants, schools, and shopping. House needs some TLC with paint and flooring. Inspections are welcome but selling as is.
